									</li>									</ol>								</li>								<li>									In <a href="2">Nadir of the Darklight</a>,									Tom and Xiu are drawn into the growing conflicts of the hell that has forgotten that it isn’t real, and eventually “die” and lose their memories of reality as well.									<ol>										<li>											In <a href="2/1">Part 1</a>,											the ghost of the wizard Thomas recruits supporters to free his imprisoned body by recounting the story of how he Inadvertently began this war against the Orcs.										</li>										<li>											In <a href="2/2">Part 2</a>,											humble farmer John is conscripted into the Chalman army to fight the Orcs, where he meets a camp follower "Tamara" who is secretly the wizard Thomas.										</li>										<li>											In <a href="2/3">Part 3</a>,											John joins Thomas' ragtag resistance group to seek out another ancient magician, the "Pseudo-Witch", and learns the terrible truth about their world along the way.										</li>									</ol>								</li>								<li>									In <a href="3">Rising of the Darklight</a>,									Tom and Xiu are reincarnated within the virtual afterlife, and play a part in unchaining the tortured soul for whom it was first built, who in turn destroys all of it from inside.									<ol>										<li>											In <a href="3/1">Part 1</a>,											half-elven Murdock ventures from the elf-lands in search of his human father, where he is recruited into the Church of the Eldest and discovers a sinister vampire plot.										</li>										<li>											In <a href="3/2">Part 2</a>,											Murdock discovers the Vampire Queen's lieutenant is his half-sister, and sways her to his side, before a war breaks out between vampires and elves.										</li>										<li>											In <a href="3/3">Part 3</a>,											Murdock and Annabelle follow after the fleeing Vampire Queen and the abducted Elven King, where they witness the rebirth of the Queen of Hell.										</li>									</ol>								</li>							</ol>						</li>					</ol>				</section><? require $_SERVER['DOCUMENT_ROOT'] . "/includes/footer-global.php" ?>